cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with pedestrian detection using deep learning methods in computer vision and robotics, which are the main topics covered by the sub-categories cs.CV and cs.RO. The use of deep reinforcement learning is also a key aspect of the paper, which makes cs.AI a likely sub-category. The paper also compares its method with state-of-the-art methodologies, which suggests that it could be relevant to the sub-categories cs.LG and cs.CR, which deal with machine learning and cryptography, respectively.
